{"tid":270865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港國民教育]魔宮煞星傅滿洲","createTime":"2017-06-04T15:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T23:48:36.000Z","uid":66618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"518056b22beb755b7fb3fbe4b12b1f60fcd95c18","tid":270865,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"傅滿洲、福滿洲博士（英文：Dr.Fu Manchu），是英國推理小說作家薩克斯&middot;羅默（Sax Rohmer）創作的傅滿洲系列小說中的虛構人物。1913年在《傅滿洲的謎團》（The Mystery of Dr. Fu Manchu）一書中首次出現。按照書中的描述，傅滿洲是一個瘦高禿頭，倒豎兩條長眉，面目陰險。這個角色還通過戲劇、電視、廣播和動漫等方式塑造超過90年。他標誌性的鬍鬚被稱作「傅滿洲式鬍鬚」（Fu Manchu moustache）。傅滿洲是西方人對黃禍恐懼的代表。<br />\n<br />\n在羅默的長短篇小說中，傅滿洲博學多才，猶如浮士德一樣，集古今中外的所有科學知識於一身。正如智慧超群的史密斯不得不承認的那樣，「傅滿洲博士是中國人奸詐取巧的絕佳象徵，是經過無數代人才能出現的一種現象。他是超級天才，假如他願意的話，他完全能夠帶來一場科學的革命。而他在漫威的漫畫裏，也被設定為中國第一反派，英雄上氣的父親。<br />\n<br />\nTHE ADVENTURES OF FU MANCHU<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F6SEjt1gzDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DF6SEjt1gzDg&d=dmiGMpdkohUS9OYNg2neOBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=4da1ec69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F6SEjt1gzDg</a>"},{"pid":"7dc55f65729a02a706f062c7f24c2c78619f1881","tid":270865,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"齊來認識中國人既性本惡，<br />\n並祝巴打能夠身心都脫華入歐，成為文明人仕"},{"pid":"6f8dedf7df5fbfd76bfd47459c1468cfbe3e91eb","tid":270865,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:12:52.000Z","msg":"大煞星之女<br />\n<br />\nDaughter of the Dragon<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fF2F2mXsRog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfF2F2mXsRog&d=dmiGMpdkohUS9OYNg2neOBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=0809b9ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fF2F2mXsRog</a>"},{"pid":"03dc993b2d9f994f15f8dcd4f8d1cde5e3868f3c","tid":270865,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid